snippet.title: TINY DUCK HUNT 3D (FIRST APPEARANCE)
snippet.description:
Next generation arcade game in a cute cartoon 3D world. Sweet graphics, nice gameplay, unique control system focused on handheld and joypad gaming.

Free demo available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3127290/TINY_DUCK_HUNT_3D/

Itch.io: https://tiger-bronnikov.itch.io/duckhunt3d
X (twitter): https://twitter.com/BronnikovTiger
